  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study the investigators aimed

        1. to investigate the prevalence of orthostatic hypotension in elderly nursing home
           residents.

        2. to investigate whether the presence of orthostatic hypotension influences the chance of
           successful rehabilitation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
